org.treetank.node.delegates
Class NodeDelegate

java.lang.Object
  org.treetank.node.delegates.NodeDelegate
All Implemented Interfaces:
INode
public class NodeDelegate
extends Object
implements INode

Delegate method for all nodes. That means that all nodes stored in Treetank are represented by an instance of the interface INode namely containing the position in the tree related to a parent-node, the related type and the corresponding hash recursivly computed.

Author:
Sebastian Graf, University of Konstanz
